Kelly Jean Van Dyke https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kelly_Jean_Van_Dyke 0 Kelly Jean Van Dyke (June 5, 1958 – November 17, 1991) was an American actress and adult film performer. She was the daughter of actor Jerry Van Dyke, niece of the actor Dick Van Dyke, and first cousin once removed of Shane Van Dyke. As an actress she was known for such television programs as My Mother the Car. Kelly_Jean_Van_Dyke ( June_5_,_1958 – November_17_,_1991 ) was an_American_actress and adult_film_performer .
